@startuml
title STUDENT.RF001 - Cadastrar Novo Aluno

actor "ADMIN / STAFF" as Staff

boundary Frontend
control StudentResolver
control StudentService
control EnrollmentService
control NotificationService
control AuditService

database PostgreSQL

Staff -> Frontend : Acessa cadastro de aluno

Frontend --> Staff : Exibe formulário completo

Staff -> Frontend : Preenche dados do aluno

Frontend -> StudentResolver : mutation createStudent(dto)

StudentResolver -> StudentService : createStudent(dto)

StudentService -> PostgreSQL : validarCPF()

alt CPF já existe

    StudentService --> StudentResolver : CPF duplicado

    StudentResolver --> Frontend : Erro validação

    Frontend --> Staff : CPF já cadastrado

else CPF válido

    StudentService -> PostgreSQL : validarEmail()

    alt Email duplicado

        StudentService --> StudentResolver : Email inválido

        StudentResolver --> Frontend : Erro validação

        Frontend --> Staff : Email já utilizado

    else Email válido

        StudentService -> StudentService : calcularIdade()

        alt idade < 18

            StudentService -> StudentService : validarResponsável()

        else idade >= 18

            StudentService -> StudentService : continuarCadastro()

        end

        StudentService -> EnrollmentService : gerarMatricula()

        EnrollmentService -> PostgreSQL : consultarCadastrosDoDia()

        PostgreSQL --> EnrollmentService : contador

        EnrollmentService --> StudentService : matrícula YYYYMMDD-XXX

        StudentService -> PostgreSQL : salvarAluno()

        PostgreSQL --> StudentService : alunoPersistido

        StudentService -> NotificationService : enviarBoasVindas()

        NotificationService --> StudentService : email enviado

        StudentService -> AuditService : registrarCriação()

        AuditService --> StudentService : log criado

        StudentService --> StudentResolver : aluno criado

        StudentResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 201

        Frontend --> Staff : Cadastro realizado

    end

end

@enduml